    <subfield code="9">arXiv</subfield>
    <subfield code="a">14 pages; v2:missing factor inserted (Eqs.82,87,89,90);spell/grammar corrected; v3:15 pages; Sect.1, Subsect.3.3 and related descriptions in Subsect.3.1 revised with citations; v4:16 pages;Sect.2 (Subsections 2.1,2.2,2.3), Sect.3, Sect.4 (Subsections 4.1,4.2), and related Sect.1 and References revised; v5:a few typos corrected; to appear in Bulg. J. Phys. 41 (2014) 142-171 (title in BJP changed)</subfield>
